Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.16,0:01:43.54,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}握ったメッセージ　That's rising hope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.55,0:01:55.26,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}揺れるがない世界　非情な現状
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:57.76,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}続く壁は何重層？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.84,0:02:00.05,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}イメージ通りなんかじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.14,0:02:02.51,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}静かに騒ぎだした本能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:05.43,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}迷路みたい　行き止まりなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.56,0:02:07.85,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}もう思考はディストーション
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:10.10,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}容赦ないね　いつの間に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.19,0:02:12.52,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}見失ったルート　暴れだす
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.57,0:02:13.90,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}Pay attention！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:15.19,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}Hey one two three
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:16.44,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}Hey what is it？Watch your step now！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.53,0:02:18.20,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}常識なんか要らない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:18.91,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}Are you serious！？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.03,0:02:20.91,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}No No No don't worry 1 2 3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:23.08,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}吹き返す　心臓のリズム
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:28.37,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}視界まだ眩んでる　それでも行かなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:35.51,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}キミが信じてる僕を裏切る わけにいかない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:37.63,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}強くクラクションが鳴る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:41.30,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}孤独なまま時が経ったって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.47,0:02:43.68,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}逃げる事覚えたって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.85,0:02:46.97,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}新しい今日が来ちゃうけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:51.35,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}この願い例え魔法が無くたって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:53.44,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}叶えなきゃ　誓った
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:56.94,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}僕はキミと　まだ見たい未来　あるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:59.32,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}泣きそうでも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:03.32,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}悔しくても 止まっていられない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.53,0:03:06.83,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}握ったメッセージ　that's rising hope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.16,0:01:43.54,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}緊握訊息　That's rising hope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.55,0:01:55.26,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}死水一般的世界 無情的現狀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:57.76,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}重重牆壁接連不斷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.84,0:02:00.05,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}與印象截然不同
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.14,0:02:02.51,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}寂靜中喧囂躁動的本能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:05.43,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}如同迷路般 停止了步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.56,0:02:07.85,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}思想也會扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:10.10,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}毫不留情 不知何時
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.19,0:02:12.52,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}一旦迷失前進指標 就會狂暴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.57,0:02:13.90,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}Pay attention！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:15.19,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}Hey one two three
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:16.44,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}Hey what is it？Watch your step now！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.53,0:02:18.20,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}並不需要常識
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:18.91,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}Are you serious！？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.03,0:02:20.91,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}No No No don't worry  One Two Three
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:23.08,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}沉默的心臟 再次傳來跳動的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:28.37,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}即使視野很混亂 但是不得不去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:35.51,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}你還相信著 我不會背叛你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:37.63,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}震撼地號角聲鳴起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:41.30,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}即使孤單著 就算時光變遷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.47,0:02:43.68,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}還是學會逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.85,0:02:46.97,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}嶄新的一天還會到來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:51.35,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}這個願望 即使沒有魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:53.44,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}我也誓要實現它
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:56.94,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}我們彼此還有眾多憧憬的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:59.32,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}所以即使想哭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:03.32,OP-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8\blur7}還是心有不甘 也不能止步不前
